Package org.openimaj.experiment.dataset.split

Interfaces describing objects which can provide different splits of a dataset.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KWaySplitProvider<OUT extends Dataset<?>>
    An object that breaks a dataset into K splits.
    TestSplitProvider<OUT extends Dataset<?>>
    An object that can provide a test dataset.
    TrainSplitProvider<OUT extends Dataset<?>>
    An object that can provide a training dataset.
    ValidateSplitProvider<OUT extends Dataset<?>>
    An object that can provide a validation dataset.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GroupedRandomSplitter<KEY,INSTANCE>
    This class splits a GroupedDataset into subsets for training, validation and testing.

Package org.openimaj.experiment.dataset.split Description

Interfaces describing objects which can provide different splits of a dataset. A split is a non-overlapping subset of a dataset.
